headline: TD Cowen Maintains Buy Rating on RTX Corporation (RTX), Lifts PT
summary: Analysts at TD Cowen revealed their optimism for RTX Corporation (NYSE:RTX) on May 24, increasing the price target from $142 to $155 while keeping a Buy rating.
